[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]（MLB）中，'''「20-20-20」俱樂部'''指的是單季同時達成至少20支[[二壘安打|二壘安打]]、至少20支[[三壘安打|三壘安打]]及至少20支[[全壘打|全壘打]]的[[打者|打者]]俱樂部<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Statistics|journal=Baseball Digest|volume=49|issue=5|pages=8|publisher=Century Publishing|location=Evanston, Illinois|date=May 1990|issn=0005-609X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jC4DAAAAMBAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=20-20-20%20club&f=false|accessdate=2012-07-06|quote=How many players have had 20 or more doubles, triples, and home rune in the same season? ... To further narrow the 20–20–20 club, has anybody else, besides Mays added 20 stolen bases ...}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=At Second, He's First In the Class|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1990/07/09/sports/at-second-he-s-first-in-the-class.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|date=1990-07-09|accessdate=2012-08-09|first=Leonard|last=Koppett|newspaper=The New York Times|quote=The first year, I almost made the 20-20-20 club: I had 19 triples and 19 homers, and more than 20 stolen bases.|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105045516/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/07/09/sports/at-second-he-s-first-in-the-class.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Granderson joins elite homer-double-triple club, helping Tigers beat Seattle|url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/2007-09-07-3913329224_x.htm|date=2007-09-07|accessdate=2012-08-11|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=USA Today|quote=Granderson [was] just the sixth player since 1900 with at least 20 home runs, 20 doubles and 20 triples in one season..., join[ing] the 20-20-20 club.}}</ref>。1911年，{{le|弗蘭克·舒爾特|Frank Schulte}}成為第一位達成此紀錄的球員。而最近達成20-20-20這個里程碑的球員，是2007年球季的[[柯蒂士·格蘭德森|柯蒂士·格蘭德森]]和[[吉米·羅林斯|吉米·羅林斯]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/20-homers-20-triples-20-doubles-20-steals-club|title=No player has joined this exclusive club since '07|first=Thomas|last=Harrigan|date=2020-03-15|accessdate=2020-05-24|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419062301/https://www.mlb.com/news/20-homers-20-triples-20-doubles-20-steals-club|archivedate=2020-04-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該年也是首次有兩位球員在同一球季裡完成20-20-20的成就<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=ZORLDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT138|title=Incredible Baseball Trivia: More Than 200 Hardball Questions for the Thinking Fan|publisher=Simon and Schuster|date=2019-03-05|last=Nemec|first=David|author-link=David Nemec|page=138|isbn=9781683582342|access-date=2020-09-17|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918103557/https://books.google.ca/books?id=ZORLDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT138|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

截至目前為止，20-20-20俱樂部成員僅有7名球員<ref>{{Cite news|title=Granderson's 20th steal puts Tigers center fielder in select company|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|work=ESPN|agency=Associated Press|date=2007-09-09|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3011789|accessdate=2010-12-08|quote=Granderson has 22 triples—the most by a Tiger since Ty Cobb had 24 in 1917—and 36 doubles. He hit his 20th homer Friday, becoming the sixth player since 1900 in the 20-20-20 club and the first since Kansas City's George Brett in 1979.|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223235403/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3011789|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這七名球員中，有五人是左打、一人右打，還有一人是{{le|左右開弓 (棒球)|switch hitter|兩打}}（左右開弓）。另外，[[喬治·布列特|喬治·布列特]]及[[威利·梅斯|威利·梅斯]]兩名打者還同時是[[3000安打俱樂部|3000安打俱樂部]]的成員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/H_career.shtml|title=Career Leaders & Records for Hits|work=Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2012-05-08|archive-date=2012-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014200416/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/H_career.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中梅斯也是[[500全壘打俱樂部|500全壘打俱樂部]]的成員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/HR_career.shtml|title=Career Leaders & Records for Home Runs|work=Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2012-05-08|archive-date=2010-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208132853/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/HR_career.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。舒爾特、羅林斯和[[吉姆·巴頓里|吉姆·巴頓里]]在達成此一紀錄時也贏得該季的[[美國職棒大聯盟最有價值球員獎|最有價值球員獎（MVP）]]<ref name="rollinsref"/><ref name="schulteref"/><ref name="bottomleyref"/> 。梅斯和羅林斯完成20-20-20成就的球季也達成至少30發全壘打及至少30次盜壘的紀錄，同步加入[[30-30俱樂部|30-30俱樂部]]<ref>{{cite web |title=His 30–30 club has 5 stocks as stars |url=http://www.omaha.com/article/20110417/MONEY/704179949 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130131152154/http://www.omaha.com/article/20110417/MONEY/704179949 |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2013-01-31 |date=2011-04-17 |accessdate=2012-06-24 |first=John |last=Dorfman |publisher=Omaha.com (Bloomberg News) |quote=In baseball, the club is for ballplayers who belt 30 home runs and steal 30 bases in the same season. }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Deane|first=Bill|title=Here Are Top Candidates To Join Elite '30-30' Club|journal=Baseball Digest|volume=46|issue=5|page=34|publisher=Century Publishing|location=Evanston, Illinois|date=May 1987|issn=0005-609X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DTQDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA34&dq=30-30+club#v=onepage&q=30-30%20club&f=false|accessdate=2012-07-06|quote=In 1956, Willie Mays became the second player to score a 30-30 season; a year later, he became the first to turn the trick twice.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rollins joins 30-30 club for first time|url=http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20070925&content_id=2229561&vkey=news_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi&affiliateId=CommentWidget|date=2007-09-25|accessdate=2012-06-24|first=Andy|last=Jasner|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。布列特及羅林斯在完成20-20-20的球季也打出單季超過200支安打的紀錄<ref name="rollinsref"/><ref name="brettref"/>。此外，這七名球員中有四人在他們達成20-20-20紀錄的球季，還完成20次以上的[[盜壘|盜壘成功]]，這些球員也被視為是'''「20–20–20–20俱樂部」'''的成員<ref>{{Cite news|last=Associated Press|title=Baseball: Rollins joins 20-20-20-20 club|newspaper=Honolulu Advertiser|pages=|date=2007-09-30|url=http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2007/Sep/30/br/br0941826573.html|accessdate=2010-12-08|quote=Phillies star Jimmy Rollins tripled against Washington on today and joined Curtis Granderson, Willie Mays and Frank "Wildfire" Schulte as the only players in major league history with 20 stolen bases, 20 homers, 20 triples and 20 doubles.|archive-date=2020-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913104315/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2007/Sep/30/br/br0941826573.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Granderson steals way to elite class|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20070909&content_id=2198292&vkey=news_det&fext=.jsp&c_id=det”&affiliateId=CommentWidget|date=2007-09-09|accessdate=2012-06-16|first=Tim|last=Kirby|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174951/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/print.jsp?ymd=20070909&content_id=2198292&vkey=news_det&fext=.jsp&c_id=det%E2%80%9D&affiliateId=CommentWidget|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tigers lock up outfielder Granderson with five-year, $30.25M deal|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3229965|date=2008-02-04|accessdate=2012-06-16|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|work=ESPN|quote=He joined Willie Mays and Frank "Wildfire" Schulte as the only players in major league history with 20 steals, 20 homers, 20 triples and 20 doubles. Philadelphia shortstop Jimmy Rollins became a part of the 20-20-20-20 club later in the season.|archive-date=2008-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080208055214/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=3229965|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在美國職棒聯盟的歷史上，每年都有很多球員同時打出至少20支二壘安打及20支全壘打。然而20-20-20俱樂部中所要求的三壘安打紀錄，使其變得難以達成。這是因為三壘安打的落點通常與二壘安打相似，但是球員速度要夠快才能跑出三壘安打<ref>{{cite book|last1=Koney|first1=Jackie|last2=Silva|first2=Deidre|title=It Takes More Than Balls: The Savvy Girls' Guide to Understanding and Enjoying Baseball|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IwtuBEfPx24C&pg=PA66|accessdate=2011-09-23|year=2008|publisher=Skyhorse Publishing|isbn=978-1-60239-631-9|pages=66–67|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803033557/https://books.google.com/books?id=IwtuBEfPx24C&pg=PA66|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不論是對高[[長打率|長打率]]的打者還是速度快的跑者來說，這都是項艱難的挑戰：因為高長打率的打者可能跑壘速度較慢、較常打出[[平飛球|平飛球]]（line drive）、或是把球打到牆外變成全壘打<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/archives/2010/07/bengie-molina-on-cycle-being-s.html |title=Bengie Molina on cycle: 'Being slow has never been a joke for me' |last=Grant |first=Evan |date=2010-07-16 |work=Dallas Morning News |accessdate=2012-06-23 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130181714/http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/archives/2010/07/bengie-molina-on-cycle-being-s.html |archivedate=2012-01-30 }}</ref><ref name="reyes">{{cite web|title=Reyes turning the triple into an art form|url=http://newyork.mets.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20110620&content_id=20761300&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|date=2011-06-20|accessdate=2012-06-23|first=Anthony|last=DiComo|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|quote=Citi Field['s] high walls and quirky outfield dimensions...has certainly played a role in the frequency of Reyes' triples, not only allowing a greater percentage of them to fall safely on the outfield grass, but also ensuring that only a few of his line drives will clear the fence for homers.<br>The only thing a hitter can control...is his baserunning effort}}{{Dead link}}</ref>；而跑速快的跑者也許能跑比較多壘包，但也可能沒辦法把球打得夠遠<ref name="reyes"/>。

由於20-20-20俱樂部難以達成使其成員稀少，因此{{le|棒球文摘|Baseball Digest}}在1979年將其評為「美國職棒大聯盟裡最獨特的俱樂部」（the most exclusive club in the Majors）<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Wertz|first=Dennis M.|title=The Most Exclusive Club in the Majors: Since 1900, only four players have collected 20 doubles, triples, and homers in one season|journal=Baseball Digest|volume=38|issue=10|pages=60–61|publisher=Century Publishing|location=Evanston, Illinois|date=October 1979|issn=0005-609X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qzQDAAAAMBAJ&printsec=frontcover#v=onepage&q=It%20may%20sound%20like%20an%20eye%20test%20for%20a%20three-eyed%20monster%20in%20a%20sci-fi%20movie%2C%20but%20the%20combination%20of%2020-20-20%20is%20the%20criterion%20for%20membership%20in%20one%20of%20baseball's%20most%20exclusive%20clubs.&f=false|accessdate=2012-07-06|quote=It may sound like an eye test for a three-eyed monster in a sci-fi movie, but the combination of 20-20-20 is the criterion for membership in one of baseball's most exclusive clubs.}}</ref>，而20-20-20俱樂部在當時僅有四名成員。俱樂部現有成員中有五人具有[[美國國家棒球名人堂暨博物館|棒球名人堂]]的資格，其中三人已{{le|棒球名人堂成員列表|List of members of the Baseball Hall of Fame|名列其中}}（有兩人在第一次票選中就被選上）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/hof.shtml|title=Baseball Hall of Fame Inductees|work=Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2016-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127105121/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/hof.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。球員必須要至少有十年以上大聯盟資歷，並至少要在退休後五年或是逝世六個月後才有票選資格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://baseballhall.org/hall-famers/rules-election/bbwaa|title=Rules for Election|publisher=National Baseball Hall of Fame and Museum|accessdate=2016-10-08|archive-date=2010-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530074537/http://baseballhall.org/hall-famers/rules-election/bbwaa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。剩下兩名球員因為他們退休未滿五年而尚未擁有入選名人堂的資格。

